Rodney Anton WILLIAMSON, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 12-10633. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 15, 2013. Case below, 706 F.3d 405 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
